Tags docs¶

class TagsAPI(flightplandb)¶

Related to flight plans. Accessed via tags().

fetch() → List[flightplandb.datatypes.Tag]¶

Fetches current popular tags from all flight plans. Only tags with sufficient popularity are included.

Returns

A list of the current popular tags.

Return type

List[Tag]
